snippet.title: 99 Spirits English Gameplay Preview
snippet.description:
Presenting the first look into 99 Spirits English gameplay.
Footage is from a pre-alpha version, all content is subject to change.
Please support the ongoing English localization of the puzzle RPG 99 Spirits:
